Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.90,0:01:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在霍夫曼那裡見到埃洱了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.20,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:36.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的精神還不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他現在正在艾爾大陸上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最近得到的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們運氣真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.90,0:02:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到那麼大的海嘯竟然都沒有受什麼傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德和雷恩...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你最重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.60,0:03:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船晃得還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.30,0:03:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想不想出去走走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜....妳也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片森林.....感覺真詭異耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一路上，似乎都沒有看到什麼小動物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片森林完全感覺不到生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不會又是因為...魔石索沙的影響吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看應該錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...照妳這麼說...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林裡的動物難道...全遭不測了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼味道啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是受到魔石索沙影響所冒出的毒氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.20,0:04:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一情況比我以前看到的還要糟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那些魔物的魂魄的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小長?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼!聞了我就想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小圓?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這一帶...現在已經變成這些妖怪的棲息地了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的棲息地?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾.....這片大地也保不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.50,0:05:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們現在還是盡快離開的好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒有希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們搭船去拉克爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地方....至少比較安全一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的很感謝各位對我們的關心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們早就已經決定要留在這片土地了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長老
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們從出生就是在這裡長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於我們來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片大地就像我們的母親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的母親...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你們忍心拋下已經生病的母親離開嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們活到這把年紀從來沒離開過這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都愛這片土地，也以這片土地為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們生長的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:03.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的要死的話，也要死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話啊.....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太奇怪了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這樣是不對的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這並不表示我們放棄希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並不是放棄希望而一心等死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而是我們還一直抱著一絲希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『當這塊大地－艾克斯貝爾...\N受到欺凌，民不聊生的時候...』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『便會出現一位異國打扮的勇者』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『勇者高舉著光劍，拯救苦難的人民』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的...勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奧佩拉...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天慢慢涼了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借我看一下?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦...好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這似乎還可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.80,0:07:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問......這是用來做什麼的?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得克勞德一路上都非常寶貝它的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.40,0:07:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪妳會不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了和遠方的人說話而發明的機器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遠方的人說話...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多遠呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和宇宙空間通話也許不太可能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是在這個行星上的話...應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們能用它跟克勞德說話嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕沒有辦法...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方必須也要有一個相同的機器才能夠通話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳現在有什麼打算?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾大陸太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在也只能折回拉克爾大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是妳想...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是雪螢火蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪螢火蟲?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近的人，都把它叫做『大地的精靈』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也認為它們是喜悅和希望的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜悅.....和希望...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像奧佩拉姐找尋埃洱奈斯特一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以靠自己去找克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道艾爾大陸現在非常危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不想逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想離開這個地方...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我還想...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再見到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見他...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何，我一定要找到他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也許比較好...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞麗奴...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾修頓...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們該不會...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然囉，我們也要和蕾娜一起去找
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.50,0:09:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為.....我們是好朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，小長?小圓?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道極不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還動得了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一定能再動的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實啊....每次看到你的時候，我都會想...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是什麼東西\N驅使你對每件事...抱持...這種信念?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要超越一座山...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.90,0:11:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一座高聳的大山...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想要超越那座山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別看我這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦袋最不靈光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受損太嚴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是一般的科學家恐怕得投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你放心，我一定能修好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德他們有沒有事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德他們在那波大海嘯來襲之前就上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.40,0:12:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想他們應該不會有事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們在海上遇到了海嘯...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可就什麼都完囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准你說這種話!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛這麼悲觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妳也用不著踢我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾利亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是魔石索沙墜落的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.30,0:12:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡的情況怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.80,0:12:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾爾利亞...過去曾經被喻為藝術之都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是艾爾大陸上最繁榮的一個城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是......自從那顆魔石掉下來之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的榮景都消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且....現在那個地方已經成了魔物出沒的魔域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們人類根本就連一步都不敢隨便靠近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些妖怪都是由魔石索沙繁衍出來的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說啊!我們就在這裡吃便當吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼話啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是才剛剛上路的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在發育餓得快嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小長跟小圓呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快，快，快，你給我乖乖的走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子再餓一點吃起便當來，才會更好吃的，艾修頓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛...塞麗奴....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們救救我啊....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼啦 蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:13:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.50,0:14:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對錯不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到克勞德的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡 克勞德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經看不到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.40,0:14:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我到這邊去找
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去那邊找...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.50,0:15:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你發出的聲音?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不.....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要.....求求你......
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.50,0:16:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你....救我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見到克勞德以前...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能死...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還好吧?蕾娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.40,0:16:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來吧，現在由我來對付你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空破斬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.30,0:17:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會守住蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是絕對不會讓你傷害她的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜，妳快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是為了保護同伴才努力撐住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想....他一定會好好的守護妳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此他才能保有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳吼破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳說中的...勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克勞德...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，蕾娜...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說古書解讀出來了，是真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才剛剛解開...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容到底是怎麼說的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古書裡到底寫了些什麼?奇斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一個...我在路上再告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最要緊的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.80,0:19:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得立刻通知克勞德他們這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:20:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個機械.....到底是什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.50,0:20:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來魔石還可以啟動一個機械啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.70,0:20:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它應該原本就是一種用來啟動機械的能量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個情況現在好像越來越超出我們想像了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔石...索沙...

